        "audio": "Voiceover: 'Introducing CloudSoft Comforts. Because their world should be as soft as a parent's touch.'"
      },
      "scene_3": {
        "visual": "A happy, active baby crawling effortlessly across a rug. The camera zooms in on the legs to show zero red marks or indentations.",
        "audio": "Voiceover: 'No chafing, no restrictions. Just 360 degrees of breathable, cloud-like comfort.'"
      },
      "scene_4": {
        "visual": "CloudSoft Logo appears with a 'Claim Your Free Sample' button.",
        "audio": "Voiceover: 'CloudSoft. The comfort they deserve and the peace of mind you need.'"
      }
    },
    "social_media_posts": [
      {
        "platform": "Instagram",
        "format": "Carousel Post",
        "image_concept": "Slide 1: Smiling baby in a CloudSoft diaper. Slide 2: Macro shot of the breathable, hypoallergenic material. Slide 3: Quote from a pediatrician or parent tester.",
        "caption": "Say goodbye to red marks and restless nights! 👋 Our new CloudSoft diapers move WITH your baby, not against them. Tap the link in our bio to claim your free sample pack today! ☁️👶 #BabyComfort #CloudSoftBaby #ParentingHacks"
      },
      {
        "platform": "TikTok",
        "format": "Short-form Video",
        "image_concept": "A popular parenting influencer doing a 'Stretch Test' comparing a standard diaper to the CloudSoft diaper, highlighting the flexible waistband and soft interior.",
        "caption": "The stretch test speaks for itself. Finally, a diaper that doesn't leave red marks! 🍼✨ #MomTok #DadTok #BabyEssentials"
      }
    ]
  },
  "alternatives": [
    {
      "approach": "Humor and Mess-Prevention Focus",
      "description": "Focusing on the messiness of parenting and how this comfortable diaper also securely contains 'blowouts'.",
      "pros": "High shareability, high relatability, and strong viral potential on platforms like TikTok.",
      "cons": "May dilute the premium 'ultimate comfort' messaging by pivoting to functional mess control."
    },
    {
      "approach": "Eco-Friendly Comfort Focus",
      "description": "Highlighting sustainable, plant-based materials alongside the physical comfort.",
      "pros": "Appeals strongly to environmentally conscious parents willing to pay a premium.",
      "cons": "Increases customer acquisition cost by narrowing the target demographic."
    }
  ],
  "notes": [
    "Campaign assumes a digital-first marketing budget with no traditional TV spend.",
    "A/B testing is required for video ad voiceovers to determine the highest converting tone.",
    "Ensure all product claims regarding 'hypoallergenic' materials are legally vetted and certified."
  ],
  "check_points": [
    "1. Finalize brand identity, packaging design, and legal disclaimers.",
    "2. Complete production of video scripts and static digital assets.",
    "3. Launch influencer seeding phase (distribute 500 PR boxes to micro-influencers).",
    "4. Deploy paid digital ads and monitor cost-per-acquisition (CPA) daily."
  ],
  "next_steps": [
    "Review and approve the proposed JSON campaign structure and concepts.",
    "Allocate initial ad spend across Instagram and TikTok.",
    "Engage a creative video production agency to execute the video ad script."
  ]
}
```

